items.name: EvanNav_SV
items.description: EvanNav_SV 是 EvanNav的超级简化版本（Super Vanilla），将完整导航系统的精华浓缩为单个 HTML 文件。这款轻量级网址收藏管理工具继承了原版的核心功能和优雅设计，同时大幅提升了便携性和易用性。

items.name: Data-Visualisation
items.description: A Python project showcasing data visualization using NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib, and Seaborn. It covers data preprocessing, statistical analysis, and creating insightful visualizations like line plots, heatmaps, box plots, and more. Ideal for learning and practicing data analysis and visual storytelling.
